text: Tijs is a Dutch male given name, which is a derivative form of the English name Timothy. It may refer to: *Tijs Goldschmidt (born 1953), Dutch writer and evolutionary biologist *Tijs Tinbergen (born c. 1947), Dutch filmmaker *Tiësto (born Tijs Michiel Verwest, 1969), Dutch DJ Category:Dutch masculine given names
title: Tijs
